mailsync (5.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=high

  * new upstream:
    * completely reengineered and source split in smaller and
      more comprehensible chunks
    * synching of mailboxes containing submailboxes and messages should
      be possible now
    * documented diff mode
    * Solaris autoconf
  * debian:
    * built against libc-client2003-dev (thanks LaMont)     closes: #182245
    * built against lib-client2003 (J.Guasch)               closes: #185168
    * libc-client2003-dev now depends on libkrb5-dev        closes: #181353
      (thanks R.Murray)
  
 -- Tomas Pospisek <tpo_deb@sourcepole.ch>  Fri, 21 Mar 2003 15:45:28 +0100

